21
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,140
Is it pretty?

22
00:02:32,140 --> 00:02:33,380
Yes.

23
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,580
Come on, let's go down to see it.

24
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:37,260
