to give me half of the money.

43
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:29,300
Mark my words.

44
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:31,580
You're old, and you'll die ahead of me.

45
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:37,140
I won't sell the house.

46
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,420
