104
00:07:32,820 --> 00:07:35,180
She even wishes me to die ahead of her.

105
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:36,340
Don't even think about it!

106
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:39,260
A life for a life,

107
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:40,020
