130
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:29,700
Sir.

131
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:30,620
Those two boys.

132
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:34,380
How dare

133
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,620
